%H A370481 <a href="/index/Rec#order_03">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (5,-7,3).
%F A370481 a(n) = 4*a(n-1) - 3*a(n-2) + 2 with a(0) = 33 and a(1) = 102 for n >= 2.
%F A370481 a(n) = 10*A237930(n) + 3 - n.
%F A370481 a(n) = 35*3^n - n - 2. - _Hugo Pfoertner_, Mar 31 2024
%F A370481 From _Elmo R. Oliveira_, Jul 20 2026: (Start)
%F A370481 G.f.: (33 - 63*x + 32*x^2)/((1 - x)^2*(1 - 3*x)).
%F A370481 E.g.f.: exp(x)*(35*exp(2*x) - (x + 2)).
%F A370481 a(n) = 5*a(n-1) - 7*a(n-2) + 3*a(n-3). (End)
%e A370481 a(1) = 3*33 + 3 = 102.
%e A370481 a(2) = 3*102 + 5 = 311.
